com.sonf.core.filter

类 DefaultFilterChain

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sonf.core.filter.DefaultFilterChain
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IFilterChain

    public class DefaultFilterChain
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFilterChain
    Default implementation of IFilterChain used in each session, it will be built when session is ready for I/O operations. All filters added into this chain is selected out from controller's FilterChainBuilder
